<dl id="un1013aj"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="un1" href="#un1013">UN1: </a>  <a href="../../FF/unbs/un1all.htm#un1013aj"> (NLI.3) 13(aj)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Christ &mdash; blended ~ <small>Red</small></blockquote> <dd class="well"> <ul class="list-inline" id="un1013aj"> <li>Ulysses unlocated</li> </ul> <blockquote class="sources">A Study in Christian Gnosticism&rdquo; 332: &ldquo;Now Jesus being <font color="green">[re-]</font> generated from the Virgin <font color="green">[Repentant Sophia]</font> by the energising of God <font color="green">[the mystery of the new birth, or bringing to birth of the perfect body of purity]</font>, was wiser and purer and more righteous than all men; <font color="green">[so]</font> the <mark>Christ-blended-with-Sophia</mark> <font color="green">[the two-in-one, male-female Presence]</font> descended on him, and he became Jesus Christ.&rdquo; <small> <a name="THRdec1908" href="/udra/udex.htm#THRdec1908"><cite title="source">The Theosophical Review</cite></a> (December 1908), G. R. S. Mead, &ldquo;The Secret of Jesus</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
